50|$|<b>Ground</b> <b>Wave</b> {{propagation}} is {{a method}} of radio frequency propagation that uses the area between {{the surface of the}} earth and the ionosphere for transmission. The <b>ground</b> <b>wave</b> can propagate a considerable distance over the earth's surface particularly in the low frequency and medium frequency portion of the radio spectrum. <b>Ground</b> <b>wave</b> radio propagation is used to provide relatively local radio communications coverage.|$|E
